            checksums.sha256

        evidence/
            raw/
            photos/
            logs/
            operator_notes/

        derived/
            timelines/
            extracts/
            figures/

        commands/
            collection.log
            replay.sh

        reports/
            initial_triage.md
            handoff.md


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ADD EVIDENCE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Add a file to an existing case.

Required:
    --case CASE_ID
        Existing case identifier.

    --file PATH
        Path to the file being added.

    --type TYPE
        Evidence classification.

        Available types:
            raw
            photo
            log
            note

Example:
    ${SCRIPT_NAME} add \\
        --case GC_20260715_184500_UTC_link_loss \\
        --file ./vehicle.log \\
        --type log \\
        --apply


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
COLLECT
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Collect data directly into an existing case.

Required:
    --case CASE_ID
        Existing case identifier.

Optional:
    --profile NAME
        Collection profile to execute.

Example:
    ${SCRIPT_NAME} collect \\
        --case GC_20260715_184500_UTC_link_loss \\
        --profile general \\
        --apply


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VERIFY
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Validate case structure, required artifacts, and evidence integrity.

Required:
    --case CASE_ID
        Existing case identifier.

Example:
    ${SCRIPT_NAME} verify \\
        --case GC_20260715_184500_UTC_link_loss


────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
BUNDLE
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Package an existing case into a portable .tar.gz archive.

Required:
    --case CASE_ID
